latest_reviews.title: Exactly what I wanted
latest_reviews.review: This is fabulous paper, I use it to make my traveler's notebook inserts. It's very smooth for writing and a good thickness which keeps most pens (even Papermate flairs) from bleeding with minimal shadowing. I like this size because it's fewer cuts for a cahier size and no cuts for an A5.
